    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826560/extras/3dc5f6a632dc86fbc187450b87e24203.avif?t=1739981069\" width=610 height=222 /></span><br><strong>Once Upon a Time... Life : Origins </strong><br>Dive into the world of a well-known franchise, Hello Maestro Once Upon a Time...,  that taught an entire generation about the human body. Along the way you will meet many characters from the series and get the opportunity to help them out and learn from them. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826560/extras/f3cb1e9f0cb140580de05a7ae06a2a63.poster.avif?t=1739981069\" width=610 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826560/extras/f3cb1e9f0cb140580de05a7ae06a2a63.webm?t=1739981069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826560/extras/f3cb1e9f0cb140580de05a7ae06a2a63.mp4?t=1739981069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Play in Co-op</strong><br>Thanks to asymmetrical co-op, parents and children can discover the secrets of the human body together. Once Upon a Time... Life  : Origins , while also fun for solo players, really starts to shine when two players cooperate in solving puzzles and helping out in various parts of the body. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826560/extras/964ca7bb72eefc6bf4ac8416fecc7728.poster.avif?t=1739981069\" width=610 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826560/extras/964ca7bb72eefc6bf4ac8416fecc7728.webm?t=1739981069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826560/extras/964ca7bb72eefc6bf4ac8416fecc7728.mp4?t=1739981069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Learn Through Fun</strong><br>The adventure will take you to the different systems of the human body where you can learn how each of them work. During your journey, you will visit places like the respiratory system, the gastric system, and the nervous system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826560/extras/4460cd581ea3f235abc7dcc772661868.avif?t=1739981069\" width=610 height=222 /></span><br><strong>Solve Puzzles and Face Challenges</strong><br>A variety of puzzles will keep you entertained throughout the story. The game offers two kinds of puzzles – platforming challenges and logical riddles that are great fun to solve together or solo.",
